org.enquery.encryptedquery.schema.query

Class QuerySchema

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.enquery.encryptedquery.schema.query.QuerySchema
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class QuerySchema
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class to hold information about a query schema.

    The query schema is designed to be instantiated via the QuerySchemaBuilder or a loader.
